ocal/2020/03/24/two-elderly-virginians-are-states-8th-9th-coronavirus-deaths/|title=Two elderly Virginians are state's 8th, 9th coronavirus deaths|website=WSLS10|language=en-US|access-date=2020-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325035022/https://www.wsls.com/news/local/2020/03/24/two-elderly-virginians-are-states-8th-9th-coronavirus-deaths/|archive-date=March 25, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Henry County, Virginia|Henry County]]\n|3\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Hopewell, Virginia|Hopewell (city)]]\n|9\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Isle of Wight County, Virginia|Isle of Wight County]]\n|18\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[James City County, Virginia|James City County]]\n|111\n|2<ref name=\"WTVR-March22\">{{cite web |last1=Staff |title=Virginia COVID-19 deaths jump to 6 after 3 Peninsula women die |url=https://www.wtvr.com/news/coronavirus/virginia-covid-19-deaths-jump-to-6-after-3-peninsula-women-die |publisher=[[WTVR-TV]] |accessdate=March 22, 2020 |date=March 22, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200323040858/https://www.wtvr.com/news/coronavirus/virginia-covid-19-deaths-jump-to-6-after-3-peninsula-women-die |archive-date=March 23, 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref name=\"Daily Press March 22\">{{cite web |title=Update: 3 Coronavirus deaths reported in Peninsula Health District |url=http://www.dailypress.com/virginiagazette/va-vg-coronavirus-march-22-20200322-gpwsquh5nnhy3fo4w7cv6mz3gm-story.html |website=Daily Press |accessdate=March 22, 2020 |date=March 22, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322221603/https://www.dailypress.com/virginiagazette/va-vg-coronavirus-march-22-20200322-gpwsquh5nnhy3fo4w7cv6mz3gm-story.html |archive-date=March 22, 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[King and Queen County, Virginia|King and Queen County]]\n|1\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[King George County, Virginia|King George Cou